- if @likes.present?
  %ul
    %p.like-title お気に入り一覧
    - @likes.each do |like|
      .like-content
        .like-content-box
          = link_to item_path(like.item.id) do
            .item-image
              -# = image_tag like.item.images.first
            .item-body
              .item-name
                = like.item.item_name
              .item-price
                = "￥#{like.item.price}"
- else 
  %h1
    お気に入りに追加した商品はありません
    